  ✓ Build a small reproducible computation under code/ to demonstrate the structural degree of freedom: fixed later gain with arbitrarily small earlier precursor contribution.
  ✓ Write REPORT.md incrementally with tagged claims, then finalize REPORT-SUMMARY.md once the verdict is stable.
